22 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 20, Chapter 77, Subchapter 1, is
23 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
24 20-77-153. Reimbursement for remote ultrasound procedures and remote
25 fetal nonstress tests.
26 (a)(1) The Arkansas Medicaid Program shall reimburse for remote
27 ultrasound procedures and remote fetal nonstress tests utilizing established
28 Current Procedural Terminology codes for remote ultrasound procedures and
29 fetal nonstress tests when the patient is in a residence or other off-site
30 location from the healthcare provider of the patient and the same standard of
31 care is met.
32 (2) Subdivision (a)(1) of this section shall apply to the fee-
33 for-service categories of the program and any managed care plan within the
34 program.
35 (b) A remote ultrasound and remote fetal nonstress test shall be
36 reimbursable when the healthcare provider uses digital technology that:
